### Footnotes

<span id="fn_493"></span>[197:1](sbe01201.htm#fr_495.md) After finishing
the Nishkevalya of the noon-libation, he explains the
vai*s*vadeva*s*astra of the third libation.

<span id="fn_494"></span>[197:2](sbe01201.htm#fr_496.md) The norm of the
Mahâvrata is the Vi*s*va*g*it, and the norm of that, the Agnish*t*oma
